        <section id="characters">
            <h2>Character Bios</h2>
            <div class="grid-container">
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <img src="/images/lordgresham-large.png" alt="Lord Gresham">
                    <div>
                        <h3>Lord Gresham</h3>
                        <p>Lord Gresham, one of The FEW, commands awe and fear throughout the galaxy. With dark hair and ocean-blue eyes that turn black during intense emotions, he is a formidable figure. His all-black uniform, devoid of decoration, features the glowing emblem of The FEW, and his dark red cape mirrors his emotional state, billowing and snapping without wind.</p>
                        <p>At his side, he carries a sword inscribed with ancient runes that glow ominously, capable of acting as both weapon and shield. Though not an officer, he works closely with the Galactic Alliance, who are honored by his presence. The FEW, a group so rare that many never encounter them, wield immense power, capable of manipulating the atmosphere and creating weather phenomena with ease.</p>
                        <p>Lord Gresham's strategic mind and unyielding will have led his people through countless trials. Despite his stoic exterior, he found an unexpected friend in Commander Alexander Levi. Modeled after a knight, Gresham is dedicated to eradicating evil and maintaining order in the galaxy.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <img src="/images/ladymara-large.png" alt="Lady Mara">
                    <div>
                        <h3>Lady Mara</h3>
                        <p>Lady Mara, with her lush blonde hair and violet eyes that darken with emotion, is a diplomatic force within The FEW. She wears the same all-black uniform with the glowing emblem, and her dark red cape reacts to her feelings. Her blue-glowing sword with ancient runes symbolizes her power and authority.</p>
                        <p>Mara is known for her compassionate and empathetic nature, often using her words to resolve conflicts. However, she is fierce in her pursuit of justice and the greater good. Her relationship with Lord Gresham is one of deep loyalty and complex emotions, embodying the balance between fire and water within the FEW.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-item">
                    <img src="/images/commanderlevi-large.png" alt="Commander Levi">
                    <div>
                        <h3>Commander Levi</h3>
                        <p>Commander Levi wears a space military suit that is dark blue with white and silver markings. He has light brown hair and green eyes. Friendly and charismatic, he knows every crew member's name and strengths. He can work with anyone and makes sure to bond with his crew, earning their respect and admiration. Modeled after a knight, Levi is friendly, kind, and always willing to help, yet stern in his beliefs. His strategic mind and compassion make him a natural leader, balancing duty with camaraderie.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
